                         |CKOChase
|GKO================================================================

|YKOChase is a toggle that indicates whether you
wish to pursue your prey should he leave the
room. The prey may move in a way you cannot
handle, such as through magical teleportation,
and you will be unable to follow. Otherwise,
when he flees, and you pursue him, you will be
able to track his scent.

|RKOSyntax: |YKBchase
